terraform/
├── bootstrap/
│   └── main.tf              # shared S3 backend bucket
│
├── envs/
│   ├── dev/
│   │   ├── backend.tf
│   │   └── main.tf
│   ├── stage/
│   │   ├── backend.tf
│   │   └── main.tf
│   └── prod/
│       ├── backend.tf
│       └── main.tf
│
└── versions.tf

Deployment Order (Important)
cd envs/dev
terraform init -reconfigure
terraform apply

cd ../stage
terraform init -reconfigure
terraform apply

cd ../prod
terraform init -reconfigure
terraform apply

Each environment:

Has isolated state

Can be destroyed independently

Cannot accidentally modify another env